{"tid":1981000,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"又到公開試季節，我都分享下當年Retake經歷","createTime":"2020-04-20T12:06:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-09T23:25:52.000Z","uid":356561,"like":13,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"5f0ac952027674e2d97763eb24482629a1238513","tid":1981000,"uid":356561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T12:06:20.000Z","msg":"今日第一日開account，各位多多指教。見到就黎考DSE，又見到呢度有唔少retaker，等我又分享下retake嘅經歷。<br />\n<br />\n我係舊制A-level文科，07年AL成績唔理想，結果Jupas no offer (LU都冇)。去左樹仁報名，最後有offer比我，但我心有不甘，最後決定retake。最後結果︰<br />\n<br />\n<strong>07年</strong>                                      <br />\n中化︰D                                                              <br />\nUE: E        <br />\n中史︰C                                <br />\n世史 (用英文考)︰D                             <br />\n經濟︰E                                             <br />\n                                                          <br />\n <strong> 08年</strong><br />\n中化︰ C  <br />\nUE:      E<br />\n中史︰冇retake<br />\n世史(改用中文考): C<br />\n經濟︰冇retake<br />\n中國文學(自己自修)︰D<br />\n<br />\n終於入左BU social science, 到而家出黎番工接近10年，中間仲讀多個HKU master。呢排回憶起當年AL嘅往事，百般滋味在心頭，但總算捱過左最艱難嘅retake一年。<br />\n<br />\n我想講，特別同各位就黎再入試場嘅retaker講，你上一年成績唔差嘅，有恆心有決心，個天總會比你入到U。<span style=\"color: blue;\">雖然retake呢一年係好難頂，見到d入左u嘅同學/friend會有妒忌、甚至唔甘心嘅感覺</span>。但你捱到呢一刻，只係等考埋DSE同放榜，再等Jupas放榜，就捱過左。<br />\n<br />\n當然，有d人可能retake但成績仍然唔理想，好似我當年有D一樣retake嘅同學咁。<span style=\"color: blue;\">但大學唔係唯一出路，社會仲有好多升學就業途徑比大家選擇，有心有能力嘅去到邊都一樣會成功</span>。<br />\n<br />\n共勉之<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5fe97f70e052e583e73bda5898ceba73a00f5e5","tid":1981000,"uid":100804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T12:09:47.000Z","msg":"你個成績舊時理科夠入engine 了"},{"pid":"b916bab8948bece1de1d8b064c0bcc2e9f0e67c5","tid":1981000,"uid":356561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b5fe97f70e052e583e73bda5898ceba73a00f5e5","tid":1981000,"uid":100804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T12:09:47.000Z","msg":"你個成績舊時理科夠入engine 了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T12:10:54.000Z","msg":"可惜我唔係理科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"feba68d9c5d1420f5ee334c46087d029efea9172","tid":1981000,"uid":53440,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T12:41:50.000Z","msg":"想問樓主讀完傳統乞食科依家有幾多錢人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n認真想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb6823957d4abd1ebb5f2e66c017ba92bcbac2dc","tid":1981000,"uid":87339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T12:44:36.000Z","msg":"hku係taught master定mphil?"},{"pid":"528899a51a73b4e2af1f523f33a5f468ec50075a","tid":1981000,"uid":356561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"feba68d9c5d1420f5ee334c46087d029efea9172","tid":1981000,"uid":53440,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T12:41:50.000Z","msg":"想問樓主讀完傳統乞食科依家有幾多錢人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n認真想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T12:52:47.000Z","msg":"接近2萬，不過就黎轉去做公務員<br />\n<br />\n不過我冇後悔，一路都想讀social science，身邊都有同學做到中學老師，超過3萬"},{"pid":"e4cc1f4c8f454f48faf0e8e6342ecb2af08466d6","tid":1981000,"uid":356561,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb6823957d4abd1ebb5f2e66c017ba92bcbac2dc","tid":1981000,"uid":87339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T12:44:36.000Z","msg":"hku係taught master定mphil?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T12:53:39.000Z","msg":"Taught master<br />\n我冇興趣讀MPhil走學術路"},{"pid":"294158872442081ff245